reviewText: UK-area DVD, does not work in American machines. Not disclosed by seller
I love this show. She's so creative and versatile by playing so many different characters.

As a comedic actor I have to say Catherine Tate is BRILLANT.  She is so funny I cannot get enough.  Her ability to go into character's such as NAN is a kick.  I absolutely love this woman and find her to be my "hero".  Two thumbs up and two big toes while we are at it - LMAO.
